Package: yml2renv
Title: YAML to .Renviron Variable Management
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", 
           email = "benjamin.peeters@pik-potsdam.de", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides utilities to manage .Renviron configuration variables
    from YAML configuration files. This package enables R packages to automatically
    adjust and rely on .Renviron variables for configuration, allowing for a more
    robust and standardized approach to environment variable management.
License: AGPL-3.0
